title: "Figure 4 — Training Data / Module Dependency Flow (drawn by Claude · 2026-04-26)"
---
flowchart LR
    Y[YAML config<br/>configs/ablation_shm/<br/>SUN_v2_*.yaml] --> T[train.py]
    T --> TC[load_config / seed / wandb]
    T --> TD[build_dataloader<br/>SUN Xian 645/72 split]
    T --> BB[DINO ViT-B/16 backbone<br/>**foundational, always on**]
    T --> AP[AttributePrototype<br/>**foundational, always on**<br/>learnable matrix P]

    BB --> Gf[global feature]
    BB --> Lf[local patch features +<br/>DINO CLS to patch attention]

    Gf --> CEg[**loss_ce_global**<br/>= CE on sim global x P x class_attr<br/>**uses AttributePrototype**<br/>weight lambda_global<br/>always on, never ablated]
    AP -.contributes.-> CEg

    Lf --> M1Gate{**M1 · Local Branch**<br/>feature_type=global+local<br/>is_attn=True}
    M1Gate -- off --> NoLoc[global-only path]
    M1Gate -- on --> M1Pool[per-attribute<br/>region pooling]

    M1Pool --> M2Gate{**M2 · DINO Prior**<br/>**REQUIRES M1 ON**<br/>is_prior=True/False}
    M2Gate -- hard --> M2H[threshold mask prior]
    M2Gate -- soft_add --> M2S[log-bias prior<br/>alpha or learnable_alpha]
    M2Gate -- off --> M2N[no prior]
    M2H --> AttrPred[local attribute prediction]
    M2S --> AttrPred
    M2N --> AttrPred

    AttrPred --> CEl[**loss_ce_local**<br/>weight lambda_local]

    AttrPred --> M4Gate{**M4 · VFA**<br/>**REQUIRES M1 ON**<br/>is_feature_aggregation=True}
    M4Gate -- on --> M4A[attribute-weighted<br/>feature aggregation]
    M4Gate -- off --> M4N[skip]
    M4A --> CEw[**loss_ce_wa**<br/>third CE pathway]

    AP --> M3Gate{**M3 · Decorrelation**<br/>independent of M1/M2/M4<br/>use_ap_loss=True/False}
    M3Gate -- on --> M3L[L_ap = norm of off-diag P^T P<br/>**applies to whole P matrix**<br/>weight ap_loss_weight w]
    M3Gate -- off --> M3N[skip]

    CEg --> Sum[**total_loss = weighted sum**<br/>lambda_g·L_g + lambda_l·L_l +<br/>lambda_w·L_wa + w·L_ap]
    CEl --> Sum
    CEw --> Sum
    M3L --> Sum

    Sum --> Opt[optimizer step<br/>AdamW + cosine LR]
    Opt --> Eval[evaluate_v2 each epoch]
    Eval --> M[per-class CZSL/U/S/H<br/>+ gamma sweep + AUSUC]
    M --> BT[BestTracker]
    BT --> Ckpt[best_h.pth /<br/>best_czsl.pth /<br/>final.pth<br/>contains ckpt 'metrics']

